tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I have severe hair fall problem and  went for consulting at Partha Banjara Hills. They have received well and Dr. Yamini  explained me the reasons and suggested treatment plans for my hair loss. She is so friendly and clarifies all the questions we have. I have already taken 2 sessions and my hair fall have been reduced and I could see regrowing hair.
I would recommend her as she is well experienced in Dental and Cosmetic problems. Thank you Dr.Yamini for your patience, follow-ups, and treatment planning.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: I have visited Partha Banjara Hills  for my hair treatment. DrYamini I was totally impressed by the way I was treated .hardly find such non Comercial doctors in this era , Friendly approach with smiling face and amazing treatment simple and gentle in her behaviour ,not only an excellent doctor and also superb human being ,very caring and soft spoken we can freely interact with her. May God bless her and best wishes for the future. Great hospitality and staff aslo

I got my crooked and crowded teeth treated, Dr.Yamini and the team were very friendly & helpful and best at what they do. Apart from having a good experience with the process, I was also glad that the hospital had an EMI option which was a relief for me.

I have an excellent experience at Partha dental Banjar hills. I have been going different dental clinics for past 15 years but I see this is best clinic and recommend every one. Doctor Yamini is been good and has best experience i beliive , she explains every thing informing plus and minus for the various options to go for.She also  treated for my son and applied braces and I see I had consulted the right doctor and clinic also had treated for my teeth. Over all I say had best experience.

I recently  visited  partha dental skin and hair Banjara hills branch due to gum issues.I am happy with the service provided by Dr.yamini who did her best with patience to ease the pain and gave an detailed  explanation of the problem and done the flap surgery in very co-operative way.We like all staff thank u for ur service.Ofcourse nice ambience n neat & hygiene well maintained place

I had a bad tooth alignment with which I couldn't give any interview for my job. I visited partha dental for a solution. I had a good interaction with Dr.Yamini. she have done a digital scan and suggested me to go for aligners.Now my treatment is done and I am so thankful to her.

Hello! I have been suffering with severe hairloss since 3 months. I had a consultation with Dr.Yamini at Partha Dental Skin and hair in banjara hills. She is so friendly and explained me all possible conditions for hairfall and suggested to go for GFC sessions. The treatment is working so well and my hair fall have been controlled. Thank you doc.

I have been facing issue of irregular teeth since 4 years. I have booked a consultation with Dr.Yamini in Partha Dental Banjara hills branch. She have explained me in detail about the causes and suggested to go for Invisalign aligners which is an advanced procedure. And the cost is also so reasonable. Now my treatment is done and I am so confident of my smile. Thank you Dr.Yamini and Partha.

I had my Dental implant done here in Partha dental Banjara hills location . Dr Yamini  had been so patient through out the treatment and clarified all my questions with so much paience and provide confidence that helps me to take a decision to go ahead with implant . Whole process just took 3 days and i am happy with my decision. Thank you so much Dr.Yamini mam.

I came with extremely painful wisdom tooth. Doctor yamini  was quick to diagnose and within 15-20 minutes she painlessly removed my wisdom tooth. I had no pain after the treatment. Very happy with their hospitality. Thank you Partha Dental
